snippet.title: The Gala Take on Johnny Depp v Amber Heard
snippet.description:
We're going to go in a little different direction today, however, we are still discussing how the MeToo Movement has gone too far. We've been watching the situation unfold between #JohnnyDepp and #AmberHeard with horror. We couldn't stay silent any longer. This is an intense case with major life-altering consequences. 

 Our podcast on The Pirates of the Caribbean: https://www.buzzsprout.com/1782512/8932044-ep-10-is-jack-sparrow-a-member-of-the-lgbtqia-community.mp3?download=true
